    <inclusivecriteria>Proven gastro-oesophageal reflux disease by either endoscopic or 24 hour pH monitoring. Antireflux surgery clinically indicated. Fit for surgery. Reflux inadequately controlled by standard medications or unwilling to take lifelong medication for reflux.</inclusivecriteria>
