    <healthyvolunteer>No</healthyvolunteer>
    <exclusivecriteria>No informed consent. Previous surgery for gastro-oesophageal reflux. Very large hiatus hernia (more than 50% of stomach in the chest). PregnantOesophageal motility disorder which precludes Nissen fundoplication.</exclusivecriteria>
