  <ethicsAndSummary>
    <summary>Multicentre prospective double blind randomized controlled trial comparing 3 surgical procedures for gastro-oesophageal reflux. All groups will undergo a clinically acceptable operation, according to standard clinical indications.

The study will be performed in multiple centres throughout Australia and New Zealand. The study will be coordinated from FMC and RAH in SA.

Patients will be recruited over a 2 year period. Follow-up will continue for up to 20 years.</summary>
